3: \n44: - [ ] Implement `.gitignore` parser\n45: - [ ] Implement file walking logic\n46: - [ ] Apply exclusion patterns\n47: - [ ] Handle edge cases (symlinks, hidden files)\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## Task 5: Implement Configuration Validation\n52: **Verifiable Output:** agent.yaml validated before packing\n53: \n54: - [ ] Define required configuration fields\n55: - [ ] Implement YAML parser\n56: - [ ] Validate agent name, version, entry point\n57: - [ ] Provide clear error messages for invalid configs\n58: \n59: ---\n60: \n61: ## Task 6: Add Progress Reporting\n62: **Verifiable Output:** Progress shown during pack operation\n63: \n64: - [ ] Implement progress bar for file collection\n65: - [ ] Implement progress bar for archive creation\n66: - [ ] Support `--verbose` detailed output\n67: - [ ] Support `--quiet` silent mode\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ## Task 7: Integrate with CLI Main Entry\n72: **Verifiable Output:** `pack` command accessible via `agentcube pack`\n73: \n74: - [ ] Register pack command in CLI main module\n75: - [ ] Update CLI help text\n76: - [ ] Ensure proper import paths\n77: \n78: ---\n79: \n80: ## Task 8: Write Unit Tests\n81: **Verifiable Output:** Unit tests pass with >80% coverage\n82: \n83: - [ ] Test argument parsing\n84: - [ ] Test archive creation for both formats\n85: - [ ] Test file collection with gitignore\n86: - [ ] Test configuration validation\n87: - [ ] Test error handling\n88: \n89: ---\n90: \n91: ## Task 9: Write Integration Tests\n92: **Verifiable Output:** Integration tests pass\n93: \n94: - [ ] Test full pack workflow\n95: - [ ] Test with sample agent projects\n96: - [ ] Test archive extraction and verification\n97: \n98: ---\n99: \n100: ## Task 10: Documentation\n101: **Verifiable Output:** Documentation complete\n102: \n103: - [ ] Add command help text\n104: - [ ] Update CLI README\n105: - [ ] Add examples to documentation\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ## Completion Criteria\n110: \n111: - [ ] All tasks 1-10 completed\n112: - [ ] Code follows project Python conventions\n113: - [ ] Tests pass with acceptable coverage\n114: - [ ] Documentation is complete\n115: - [ ] Command integrates properly with CLI\n\n(End of file - total 115 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-020 Tasks: CLI pack 命令\n\n> **Module:** `cmd/cli`  \n> **Language:** Python  \n> **Size:** M  \n> **Stage:** ST-0 initialized\n\n---\n\n## Task 1: Create Command Module Structure\n**Verifiable Output:** Directory `cmd/cli/pack/` exists with __init__.py\n\n- [ ] Create `cmd/cli/pack/` directory\n- [ ] Create `cmd/cli/pack/__init__.py`\n- [ ] Create `cmd/cli/pack/command.py` for main command logic\n- [ ] Create `cmd/cli/pack/archiver.py` for archive creation\n\n---\n\n## Task 2: Implement Command Line Interface","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775885304150,"end":1775885304164}}}}
